  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to assess the impact of the Multi Point Pacing (MPP) feature in
      the treatment of patients with QRS beetwen 100 and 130 msec in patients candidate to ICD
      implant.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
